{"tid":1610883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍翔道開槍片段曝光 便裝警實彈射幾十米外抗爭者","createTime":"2019-10-01T23:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T00:19:14.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d13c1b7ba7b227af51bd70aa2e98afac89362973","tid":1610883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:00:07.000Z","msg":"【黑色10.1】龍翔道開槍片段曝光 便裝警實彈射幾十米外抗爭者<br />\r\n<br />\r\n警務處處長盧偉聰昨晚於記者會上表示，警方在油麻地、荃灣及黃大仙3個地點，都有警員使用警槍，總共開了6槍，包括荃灣向中五生開槍。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n蘋果讀者昨日在黃大仙龍翔道與沙田坳道交界，拍下警員開槍一幕，從讀者提供的片段所見，一批防暴警及便裝警員，在街頭拘捕兩名抗爭人士，當時場面混亂，其間有一名便裝警員首先拔槍，警員制服兩名抗爭人士便一同後退，有防暴警施放催淚彈掩護撤退，其間再有一名防暴警及一名便裝警員拔出佩槍，指向前面一批在遠處的抗爭人士，警員帶同被捕人士撤離期間，其中一名穿白色T恤便裝警員開了一槍。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n讀者表示，看到一批警員突然衝出龍翔道，抗爭者四散逃走，警員制服兩人並按在地上，其後有警員拔槍指向抗爭人士，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時附近幾十米外都沒有人，之後警員在撤退期間無端開槍，聽到兩響槍聲，其中一下槍聲特別大，相信是實彈，另一下是催淚彈的聲響。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0K_7lzRUalh5rNPZH8nMVzlXiIP-f1bJrm554ghemrTck-0y37VcYI8KI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0K_7lzRUalh5rNPZH8nMVzlXiIP-f1bJrm554ghemrTck-0y37VcYI8KI&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a09fda8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dvideo_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0K_7lzRUalh5rNPZH8nMVzlXiIP-f1bJrm554ghemrTck-0y37VcYI8KI&h=fe02512a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=video_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0K_7lzRUalh5rNPZH8nMVzlXiIP-f1bJrm554ghemrTck-0y37VcYI8KI</a>"},{"pid":"fbce91107839376be792112d174e03de0a5fb859","tid":1610883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569955359_8d61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569955359_8d61.jpg&h=85d05b90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44132e6865305fbec140905407c252c686bee8d8","tid":1610883,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:05:13.000Z","msg":"38噸泥頭車撞鳩死哂佢地啦"},{"pid":"297329d50c96b5ed5654725e432f004b82ed9f55","tid":1610883,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569956278_cf31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569956278_cf31.jpg&h=3ce6e6b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cb8a6dcf788b4dd4c7ff9ef8ea6afcb204be457","tid":1610883,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZC6fNjP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZC6fNjP.jpg&h=ffa858cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e6e1ad5e192604320bd2fa679f479480126a43a","tid":1610883,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"鳩射"}]}